## NVIDIA Binary Components

The following NVIDIA components are proprietary software subject to NVIDIA's
End User License Agreements (EULAs):

- **CUDA Toolkit** - NVIDIA CUDA Toolkit EULA
- **cuDNN** - NVIDIA cuDNN Software License Agreement
- **TensorRT** - NVIDIA TensorRT Software License Agreement
- **cuTensor** - NVIDIA cuTensor Software License Agreement
- **NVIDIA Drivers** - NVIDIA Software License Agreement

By using this Nix flake to install these components, you agree to comply with
NVIDIA's applicable license terms. Full license texts are included with each
component upon installation and can also be found at:

https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/eula/
https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/cudnn/sla/
https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/tensorrt/sla/
https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cutensor/license.html

